      <description>&lt;p&gt;Partes del LInkedin.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&amp;ldquo;I think it&amp;rsquo;s blatantly obvious that power doesn&amp;rsquo;t lie where they tell you it does. pay attention to who is standing up to that. that&amp;rsquo;s who is on your side.&amp;rdquo;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Anthropic is an unacceptable risk to national security. If anyone is building the AI doom machine, it&amp;rsquo;s them. More seriously, this behavior will leave them as a footnote in AI history. &lt;a href=&#34;https://lnkd.in/gnuNmJqm&#34;&gt;https://lnkd.in/gnuNmJqm&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;a lot of people haven&amp;rsquo;t figured out how modern democracy works yet. you being able to vote for something that benefits you is like the rope winning tug of war.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
